headline: Should You Hold Amphenol Corporation (APH)?
summary: TimesSquare Capital Management, an equity investment management company, released its “U.S. Focus Growth Strategy” third-quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the third quarter, the strategy returned 3.90% (gross) and 3.69% (net) compared to 6.54% for the Russell Midcap Growth Index.
